---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Main.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <section>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">Hello! I'm [Your Name], a Finance student with a passion for coding and technology. I blend the worlds of finance and programming to create innovative solutions.</p>
      <p>My journey includes an internship at an investment bank, where I gained valuable insights into the financial industry. Simultaneously, I've been honing my programming skills, allowing me to approach problems from both financial and technical perspectives.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Skills & Interests</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Financial Analysis & Modeling</li>
        <li>Web Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)</li>
        <li>Data Analysis with Python</li>
        <li>Blockchain & Cryptocurrency</li>
        <li>Open Source Contribution</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Projects</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <a
            href="https://programming.in.th"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">PROGRAMMING.IN.TH</a>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">A platform for learning programming and algorithmic problem-solving.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/triamudomcmc"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">triamudomcmc's GitHub</a>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Collaborative projects and contributions to the Triam Udom Suksa School community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Connect With Me</h2>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/possawat/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block text-blue-600 hover:underline">/in/possawat</a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/iammarkps"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block text-blue-600 hover:underline">GitHub</a>
        <a href="/resume.pdf" download="" class="block text-blue-600 hover:underline">Download Resume (PDF)</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Heavy Rotation</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Music is a big part of my life. Here's what I'm currently listening to:</p>
      <iframe
        allow="autoplay *; encrypted-media *;"
        height="450"
        style="width:100%;max-width:660px;overflow:hidden;background:transparent;"
        sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation"
        src="https://embed.music.apple.com/th/playlist/heavy-rotation-mix/pl.pm-20e9f373919da08099a011b3fb435b93"
      ></iframe>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
